                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-8">
                        <h2 class="movie-title">Top Gun Maverick</h2>
                        <p class="movie-description">After 30 years of successful service in the Navy, United States Navy Lieutenant Pete “Maverick” Mitchell pushes the limits as a test pilot. Wanting to stay away from any mission that would tie him to the ground, Maverick finds himself training a platoon of Top Gun graduates for a special mission.</p>
                        <div class="movie-details">
                            <p><strong>Genre:</strong> Action</p>
