                        <div class="movie-poster">
                            <img src="~/images/SkyscrapperMovie.jpg" alt="Skyscraper" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-8">
                        <h2 class="movie-title">Skyscraper</h2>
                        <p class="movie-description">Former FBI agent Will Sawyer must save his family from a newly built Hong Kong skyscraper, the world's tallest skyscraper, after terrorists set the building on fire to blackmail the contractor.</p>
                        <div class="movie-details">
                            <p><strong>Genre:</strong> Action</p>
                            <p><strong>Director:</strong> Rawson Marshall Thurber</p>
                            <p><strong>Release Date:</strong> 2018-01-07</p>
