                            <p><strong>Language:</strong> English</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="movie-card">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="movie-poster">
                            <img src="~/images/ThePrestigeMovie.jpg" alt="The Prestige" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-8">
                        <h2 class="movie-title">The Prestige</h2>
                        <p class="movie-description">The plot of the film, which tells the story of two magicians who worked together at first, and then turned into rivalry and even hostility, takes place in the time period known as the Victorian Age in England of the 19th century. In addition to director Nolan, Aaron Ryder and his wife Emma Thomas took part in the production of the film.</p>
